{
  "stem": "21582.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this was-- we knew that our existence was temporary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, our legal existence was temporary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this was reserved for when-- when all the last few streets in Warsaw are cleaned of-- of Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one morning the door opens up and two SS men walk in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We thought that was the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Szabatnik, he-- he was with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was in the bunker with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, in-- when I say he was in the bunker, he was a member of those, because the bunker was shared with a larger group.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I think that most of his family either were hiding somewhere else or-- or they-- they might have already been killed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The Germans singled him out, and they took him with-- with him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And after they left, we quickly jumped into the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They took Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Szabatnik, and they asked him-- they-- they made him go from apartment to apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "See, they were afraid to-- to barge into an apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they told him to knock on the door and to say to the people, open the door.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's safe.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's a Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, he told them either in Polish or in Yiddish don't open the door, because there are two Germans.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Save yourselves.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Don't-- hide.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And, well, the Germans kind of sensed there must be some-- because all they got from all the knocking on the doors was silence.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they knew that-- that-- that there are more Jews there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So they started to beat him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they beat his head to a pulp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He never, ever ceased to say the same thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He came, he was beyond recognition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "His-- his blood was oozing from his eyes, from this ears, from his nose.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
